import React,{useState,useEffect} from "react"; import {useDispatch,useSelector} from "react-redux"; import Home from "./Home/home"; import "./rgcss.css"; import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; import { register } from "./actions/studentAdmitCardDetailsAction"; const Rgfrom =()=>{ const dispatch= useDispatch(); const history = useNavigate(); // const {saved}=useSelector(state=>state.admit); const [student,setStudent]=useState({ AddmissionID : "" , FullName : "" , UniversityRoll : "" , SectionRollNumber : "" , FatherName : "" , Semester : "" , Gender : "" , Email : "" , City : "" , State : "" , CourseType : "" , PinCode : "" , }); const {AddmissionID , FullName , UniversityRoll , SectionRollNumber , FatherName , Semester , Gender , Email , City , State , CourseType , PinCode } =student; const examFromSubmit=(e)=>{ e.preventDefault(); const myFrom = new FormData(); myFrom.set("AddmissionID",AddmissionID); myFrom.set("FullName",FullName); myFrom.set("UniversityRoll",UniversityRoll); myFrom.set("SectionRollNumber",SectionRollNumber); myFrom.set("FatherName",FatherName); myFrom.set("Semester",Semester); myFrom.set("Gender",Gender); myFrom.set("Email",Email); myFrom.set("City",City); myFrom.set("State",State); myFrom.set("CourseType",CourseType); myFrom.set("PinCode",PinCode); dispatch(register(myFrom)); } const dont=(e)=>{ setStudent({...student,[e.target.name]:e.target.value}) } useEffect(() => { // if(saved){ // history("/") // } }, [dispatch,history]) return(
) } export default Rgfrom;
